@port = 3000

###
### POST Request to create a Football society
## Expected result is the added society data
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/v1/societies HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Football Society",
  "description": "For fans and players of football, organizing matches and watching games together."
}

